			<div></div>
			<div class="!w-fit">
				<h1 class="!w-fit font-extrabold text-[60px] leading-[20px] text-[#F8D06D] opacity-100">Join the community</h1>
				<p class="!text-left">
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. Est laboriosam perferendis id ducimus perferendis nam maiores voluptatem ut deserunt corrupti et provident neque id velit recusandae!
				</p>
				<div class="!w-fit flex gap-x-2">
					<div class="rounded-full bg-amber-200 h-14 aspect-square "/>
					<div class="rounded-full bg-amber-200 h-14 aspect-square "/>
					<div class="rounded-full bg-amber-200 h-14 aspect-square "/>
					<div class="rounded-full bg-amber-200 h-14 aspect-square "/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer> -->
	</body>
</html>

<style>

	p {
		text-align: center;
		font: normal normal bold 25px/29px Quicksand;
		letter-spacing: 0px;
		opacity: 1;
		width: 30%;
		z-index: 2;
	}

	#about-us > h1 {
		text-shadow: 0px 0px 10px #FFDF14D4;
	}

	#top-campaigns > h1 {
		text-shadow: 0px 0px 10px #FFDF14D4;
	}

	#preview-description > h1{
		text-align: left;
		font: normal normal bold 70px/20px Dosis;
		letter-spacing: 0px;
		color: #FFFFFF;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		line-height: 1;
		opacity: 1;
	}

	#preview-description > p {
		text-align: left;
		font: normal normal normal 15px/20px Quicksand;
		letter-spacing: 0px;
		width: 100%;
		color: #DFDEDE;
		opacity: 1;
	}

</style>
